text: Castle class may refer to: *Castle-class trawler, a class of ships constructed by the Royal Navy from 1916 to 1919 *Castle-class corvette, a class of ships constructed by the Royal Navy beginning in 1943 *Castle-class patrol vessel, a class of ships constructed by the Royal Navy beginning in 1980 *GWR Castle class locomotive, a class of steam locomotives of the British Great Western Railway *InterCity 125 train sets operated in the United Kingdom by Great Western Railway (train operating company) ==See also== * Castle series (disambiguation)
title: Castle class
